<paragraph id="8BDBE937FFBBC831FF47F945FD44242A" blockId="1.[136,1452,1728,1971]" pageId="1" pageNumber="202">
The protologue of 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFBBC831FE97F944FE4625D3" box="[344,509,1729,1754]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="1" pageNumber="202" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aragonense">
<emphasis id="B9103525FFBBC831FE97F944FE4625D3" box="[344,509,1729,1754]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="202">H. aragonense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
includes a complete description in Latin of this species, followed by the provenance “In monte Tolocha [Tolosa] Arragoniae: Loscos no. 341!” [sic], and a diagnosis to differentiate this species from “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFBBC831FA40F961FEB4242B" authority="Fr." authorityName="Fr." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="1" pageNumber="202" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="caesium">H. caesium Fr.</taxonomicName>
! Rb. ic. t. 163. II” (
<bibRefCitation id="EFF594C6FFBBC831FE29F88DFD4F242A" author="Scheele, A." box="[486,756,1800,1827]" pageId="1" pageNumber="202" pagination="643 - 688" refId="ref8991" refString="Scheele, A. (1863) Revisio Hieraciorum hispanicorum et pyeranicorum. Linnaea 32: 643 - 688." type="journal article" year="1863">Scheele 1863: 667–668</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BDBE937FFBBC833FF72F8A8FD5E222D" blockId="1.[136,1452,1728,1971]" lastBlockId="3.[136,1452,158,869]" lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="204" pageId="1" pageNumber="202">
We have found a relevant original material in the Willkomm herbarium at 
<collectionCode id="ED7571F2FFBBC831FBE5F8A9FBE5244F" box="[1066,1118,1836,1862]" country="Portugal" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14498" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14498" name="University of Coimbra Botany Department" pageId="1" pageNumber="202" type="Herbarium">COI</collectionCode>
. The specimen with barcode 
<collectionCode id="ED7571F2FFBBC831FF47F8D5FF032463" box="[136,184,1872,1898]" country="Portugal" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14498" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:14498" name="University of Coimbra Botany Department" pageId="1" pageNumber="202" type="Herbarium">COI</collectionCode>
00041604 bears four complete and well-developed plants, with leaves and capitula. The sheet contains also several labels, one of them is a label original of the Loscos’s herbarium, and was annotated by Willkomm as “Franc. Loscos, plantae Aragoniae australis. / 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFBBC831FE13F81DFC8124BB" authority="Scheele" authorityName="Scheele" box="[476,826,1944,1971]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="1" pageNumber="202" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aragonense">Hieracium aragonense Scheele</taxonomicName>
/ Abundant in monte / Tolosa / Leg. 186 [this number represents the year of collection, although the last digit is missing] / Det. Willkomm”. The sheet bears also a label handwritten by Scheele, annotated as: “ 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB9C833FD8DFF47FD0023D5" authorityName="Linnaeus" authorityYear="1753" box="[578,699,194,220]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="204" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">Hieracium</taxonomicName>
arragonense mihi! […]” followed by a complete description of the plant. 
<collectionCode id="ED7571F2FFB9C833FF03FF63FF642209" box="[204,223,230,256]" country="USA" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:15406" name="Harvard University - Arnold Arboretum" pageId="3" pageNumber="204" type="Herbarium">A</collectionCode>
third label is a revision label of Arvet–Touvet, and is annotated as: “Sect. Cerinthoidea! Gr. Microcerinthea! / 
<taxonomicName id="4C6492B4FFB9C833FF47FE8FFE13222D" authority="Scheele" authorityName="Scheele" box="[136,424,266,293]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" genus="Hieracium" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="3" pageNumber="204" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="aragonense">Hier. aragonense Scheele</taxonomicName>
! / forma! / Arv.– 
<collectionCode id="ED7571F2FFB9C833FDABFE8FFDCD222D" box="[612,630,266,292]" name="Tavera, Department of Geology and Geophysics" pageId="3" pageNumber="204">T</collectionCode>
.” (
<figureCitation id="135FF5B2FFB9C833FD5DFE8FFD6F222D" box="[658,724,266,292]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[136,229,2028,2050]" captionTargetBox="[234,1353,187,2001]" captionTargetId="figure-24@2.[234,1353,187,2001]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Lectotype of Hieracium aragonense Scheele in COI (barcode COI00041604).—Image by courtesy of the University of Coimbra (Herbarium COI), reproduced with permission." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5413221" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5413221/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="204">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<caption id="DF1BB9BFFFB8C832FF47F869FD122B2F" ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5413221" ID-Zenodo-Dep="5413221" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5413221/files/figure.png" pageId="2" pageNumber="203" startId="2.[136,229,2028,2050]" targetBox="[234,1353,187,2001]" targetPageId="2">
